en_850947_0	The people of Dodangoda, Kalutara were provided with a community hall through phase II  of the Gammadda 100-Day movement.
en_850947_1	The villagers of Himbutuwila in Dodangoda, Kalutara had to face a myriad issues due to the absence of a common area for the locals to gather during a public event.
en_850947_2	Even though alternative locations in the village were used for this purpose, it failed to stand as a successful solution.Over 400 families in the village of Dodamgoda will benefit from the community hall provided through the Gammadda movement.
en_850947_3	Naleen Ratnayake, who resides in Australia, and JAT Holdings joined hands to contribute towards this project.The winner of an art competition which was held at the event was also felicitated.
